description: This Penthouse East Side 2 bedroom 2 bathroom condo features a Private Back Deck, Roof Rights and Roof Access via a spiral staircase, Central Air Conditioning, and In-Unit Laundry. The eat-in kitchen has granite countertops and gas cooking. The Primary Bedroom with En-Suite Bathroom and Walk-In Closet is located at the front of the building, while the 2nd bedroom is across the living room, creating separation and privacy. The living room has high-end accents including wainscotting and a Gas Fireplace. Private Storage located in the basement. 3 blocks (0.3 miles) to the Beach, and moments to The Broadway, The Playwright, Stop & Shop, Medal of Honor Park and more!
